<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Loja criada! — Plataforma de Lojas</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col">

  <header class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-4">
      <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl">Plataforma de Lojas</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-10 max-w-md w-full text-center">

      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 mb-2">Sua loja está no ar!</h1>

      <% if (lead && lead.tenant_slug) { %>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">
        Parabéns, <strong><%= lead.nome_contato %></strong>! A loja <strong><%= lead.nome_empresa %></strong> foi criada com sucesso.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6 text-left">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 mb-3">Seus dados de acesso</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-1">
          <span class="font-medium">Endereço:</span>
          <a href="https://<%= lead.tenant_slug %>.sualoja.com.br" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline">
            <%= lead.tenant_slug %>.sualoja.com.br
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-1"><span class="font-medium">Login:</span> <%= lead.email %></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-xs mt-2">A senha foi enviada para o seu email. Altere-a no primeiro acesso.</p>
      </div>

      <a href="https://<%= lead.tenant_slug %>.sualoja.com.br/admin"
         target="_blank"
         class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-xl transition mb-3">
        Acessar painel da loja →
      </a>

      <% } else { %>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">
        Seu cadastro foi registrado. Nossa equipe entrará em contato em breve para ativar sua loja.
      </p>
      <% } %>

      <a href="/onboarding" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 underline">Indicar para um amigo</a>
    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
